{"tid":1696193,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"二戰海報分享","createTime":"2019-11-06T04:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T18:04:42.000Z","uid":271960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"40e2235bff3e60b003c78a2eef51d889e9beb5cb","tid":1696193,"uid":271960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"以前打二戰個陣，大家上完戰場保到條命後返到軍營就會去附近啲pub飲杯野放鬆下，慶祝自己同隊友個日無死到。<br />\n<br />\n但係當時盟軍有種情況，就係大家一放鬆左呢，就會開始講自己個隊人點點點，講自己發夢點點點，有時仲會講之後行動嘅內容添。<br />\n而古今中外嘅社會都係充斥住仆街嘅。好多人督灰報串/做二五仔/敵軍間諜 就會無型之間攞到料，之後搞鳩你啦！<br />\n<br />\n所以官方就出左一系列嘅海報，提醒各軍兵咪亂講野啊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEWwANo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEWwANo.png&h=42bf93e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M914VNM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM914VNM.jpg&h=24ec6fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gX7Tzt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gX7Tzt.jpg&h=cf05c079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Loose_lips_sink_ships\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FLoose_lips_sink_ships&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnXxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=8c6bb8d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Loose_lips_sink_ships</a>"},{"pid":"b5ac86a527aba20aad6a0b95ca4915b0297914ca","tid":1696193,"uid":256768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T18:04:42.000Z","msg":"以前我都幾鐘意分析諷刺漫畫，加油share落去"}]}